      <description>&lt;p&gt;The latest updates, media coverage, and opinion pieces supporting the movement to abandon X/Twitter. You can also find &#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://leavex.eu/quotes/&#34;&gt;quotes and ideas&lt;/a&gt; related to this project.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;articles&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Articles &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#articles&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.thenerdreich.com/reboot-elon-musk-ceo-dictator-doge/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;&amp;lsquo;Reboot&amp;rsquo; Revealed: Elon Musk&amp;rsquo;s CEO-Dictator Playbook&lt;/a&gt;, by Gil Duran (&lt;em&gt;The Nerd Reich - 05.02.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://elpais.com/opinion/2025-02-04/musk-quiere-todo-el-poder.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Musk wants all the power&lt;/a&gt;, Editorial [es] (&lt;em&gt;El País - 04.02.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;icon relative inline-block align-text-bottom&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;?xml version=&#34;1.0&#34; encoding=&#34;utf-8&#34;?&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&lt;!-- Uploaded to: SVG Repo, www.svgrepo.com, Generator: SVG Repo Mixer Tools --&gt;&#xA;&lt;svg width=&#34;800px&#34; height=&#34;800px&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 32 32&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;g clip-path=&#34;url(#clip0_901_3111)&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;path d=&#34;M23.7627 20.1418C23.7627 20.1418 25.5627 27.4428 26.0827 29.4318C26.5727 31.3018 25.0727 31.2518 24.1527 30.6128C23.1227 29.8918 16.0027 24.8018 16.0027 24.8018C16.0027 24.8018 8.82267 29.9318 7.8326