/article/emmanuel-macron-france-paris-donald-trump-x-social-media-weapons-intelligence/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Au revoir de Paris, X !&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Politico - 16.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pasteur.fr/en/home/press-area/press-documents/institut-pasteur-decides-leave-x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;The Institut Pasteur has decided to leave X because of several serious abuses observed on the platform&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;press release - 16.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/niedersachsen/Plattform-X-Niedersaechsischer-Landtag-stellt-Aktivitaeten-ein,landtag6584.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;The Lower Saxony state parliament stops activities on X&lt;/a&gt; [de] (&lt;em&gt;NDR - 16.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.politico.eu/article/german-army-deserts-x-feud-between-berlin-elon-musk-afd/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;German army deserts X as Berlin vs. Elon Musk feud rumbles on&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Politico - 15.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.euronews.com/next/2025/01/15/french-group-encourages-mass-departure-from-elon-musks-x-platform-on-us-inauguration-day&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;French group encourages mass departure from Elon Musk&amp;rsquo;s X platform on US inauguration day&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Euronews - 15.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sttinfo.fi/tiedote/70809667/vihreat-poistuu-ensimmaisena-puolueena-viestipalvelu-xsta-nain-puheenjohtaja-sofia-virta-perustelee-paatosta?publisherId=69818932&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;The Finnish Green Party will be the first party to leave the messaging service X&lt;/a&gt; [fi] (&lt;em&gt;STT - 13.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.euractiv.com/section/politics/news/polish-presidential-candidates-discuss-eu-wide-restriction-of-x/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Polish presidential candidates discuss EU-wide restriction of X&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Euractiv - 13.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.politico.eu/article/us-steve-bannon-elon-musk-wealth-and-influence-are-weapons-to-advance-maga-aligned-goals-in-europe/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Musk’s money will help us make Europe a populist haven&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Politico - 08.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apnews.com/article/elon-musk-europe-politics-germany-uk-f50d69d0d192a2d81c95f5d64c6d4acd&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Elon Musk helped Trump win. Now he’s looking at Europe, and many politicians are alarmed&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;AP - 08.01.2025&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
